{"tid":2299680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歌舞群2,800人驗毒 專家質疑不足","createTime":"2020-11-25T03:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T03:32:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fff07dcda03fabb4ef5f2bd3bed0107523ed6120","tid":2299680,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/B5P6ZWUI5JGIRNC7LA2PY5QUMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FB5P6ZWUI5JGIRNC7LA2PY5QUMQ%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=c1113949\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FB5P6ZWUI5JGIRNC7LA2PY5QUMQ%2F&h=ccee46f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/B5P6ZWUI5JGIRNC7LA2PY5QUMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n歌舞群2,800人驗毒 專家質疑不足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bw-kp44E6Uloi3QRoEpqC0kgAak=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3GLJQ2VEVFG6ZJEJRTGD5KALPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBw-kp44E6Uloi3QRoEpqC0kgAak%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3GLJQ2VEVFG6ZJEJRTGD5KALPE.jpg&h=8bb8390d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■沙田瀝源檢測中心昨早大排長龍，有長者等候期間頭暈需由擔架床送院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府先後兩次刊憲，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：強制公眾場所貼安心碼  政府擬追蹤全民<br />\n<br />\n歌舞群組牽涉最少187名患者，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統科專科醫生梁子超認為，檢測數僅冰山一角，實際上需檢測人數「最少係𠵱家嘅三至五倍，最低限度都有6,000至7,000人」，將首14間舞廳的檢測數換算，即每間場所每日平均約8至10人到訪，數字偏低，不符一般舞廳正常運作，估計未被發現的患者遠多於187人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：闊太跳舞播毒 全港市民埋單  宴會限40人 業界：蝕60億<br />\n<br />\n傳媒在記者會上提問，是否所有相關人士均已完成檢測，陳肇始未有正面回應，僅稱日後若發現有人未按規定檢測，會考慮檢控。<br />\n<br />\n除檢測走漏大量隱形病人，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵站將派樣本樽<br />\n<br />\n各社區檢測中心亦繼續大排長龍，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。，亦正與港鐵商量在站內派樣本瓶，港鐵已證實將配合政府在指定港鐵站派樣本樽。港鐵工會港鐵新動力強烈反對，擔心會吸引人群聚集，增加乘客及職員感染風險，令港鐵成為「病毒運輸鏈」。"},{"pid":"1f986d5ba216d574c7e7a6d91f20f6e4cbcc41dd","tid":2299680,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"9b4f902ead5e5b2efc058967ac77bcf44c7cd4c1","tid":2299680,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:32:02.000Z","msg":"政府唔係好撚鐘意人驗既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}